programme.title: Kuldvillak
programme.desc: "Kuldvillak" on kaasakiskuv telemäng. Igas saates asuvad võistlustulle kolm inimest. Nad peavad valima endale sobiva teema. Kui saatejuht Eeva Esse on küsimuse esitanud, loeb võrdselt nii mängija reaktsioonikiirus kui ka teadmiste hulk. Kes kõige kiiremini reageerib, saab õiguse vastata. Õige vastus toob mängija arvele küsimuse väärtuses raha, kui aga vastaja eksib, tuleb suu rahast puhtaks pühkida! Vale vastuse korral ütleb saatejuht õige vastuse ja see aitab kodusel televaatajal ka oma teadmisi proovile panna, kaasa mängida ja seeläbi end harida. Kui mängijal õnnestub aga võita viis saadet järjest, on ta tunnistatud Kuldvillaku tšempioniks ja ta annab võimaluse järgmistele...

programme.title: Killer Siblings
programme.desc: Chilling true-crime documentary series that tells the stories of some of the most dangerous siblings that commited gruesome crimes. Through exclusive interviews and firsthand accounts, the series will try to explain what drove them to partner up and commit some of the most heinous and sophisticated homicides. The audience will have a chance to hear tales of their childhoods, details of their crimes and the investigations that put them behind bars. From teen brothers with a dream to become mass murderers, a sheriff's deputy who killed his wife's lover by employing his brothers, to delusional brothers who believed it's their duty to cleanse the world of those living in sin, and many others, these are their shocking stories.

programme.title: Forensics: The Real CSI
programme.desc: True-crime documentary series that follows the team of forensic specialists from Northumbria Police- crime scene investigators, ballistics scientists, forensic pathologists,... and reveals the crucial role they play in bringing criminals to justice. Take a look at the incredible journey of individual pieces of evidence from the moment they are found at the crime scene, through to microscopic analysis at specialist laboratories, and how important they can be for a crime investigation. Series includes real-life cases.

programme.title: Forensics: The Real CSI
programme.desc: As the victim of a violent knife attack fights for his life in hospital, Crime Scene Coordinator Jo Ward is dispatched to his home in Birmingham to lead the forensic investigation into identifying his attacker. The victim is unable to tell police what happened because he has been put in a medically induced coma, and the investigation becomes more challenging when no witnesses are prepared to give a statement to the police. Jo and her team work to gather vital evidence that could help police quickly identify and arrest the attacker.

programme.title: Forensics: The Real CSI
programme.desc: Police respond to a call of a shooting in a carpark. As dusk sets in, crime-scene coordinator Simon Flanaghan attends to find a car set back from the road, with multiple bullet holes and two men dead inside. A specialist ballistics team is called in to establish how many shooters were involved and where the gun was fired from. Meanwhile, homicide detectives from West Midlands Police work to establish a prime suspect and secure warrants to locate and arrest him. Continuing to investigate the suspect's movements after the incident, detective Lisa Shepherd follows a trail of digital evidence following the suspected getaway vehicle to a shopping centre in Birmingham. Digital, DNA and ballistic forensics combine with forensic accounting to paint a detailed picture of the murder and suggest a surprising motive. But will the evidence be enough to bring the killer to justice?

programme.title: Forensics: The Real CSI
programme.desc: A young woman arrives at a police station to report that she has been raped. She was attacked by a stranger at a derelict house in the early hours of the morning. The victim agrees to undergo a forensic examination at a Sexual Assault Referral Centre (SARC) to recover potentially critical evidence that could help identify her unknown attacker. A hunt for the unknown attacker ensues. Using a doorbell recording and CCTV footage, the police begin the hunt to bring the perpetrator to justice.

programme.title: Forensics: The Real CSI
programme.desc: At midday on a busy high street in Birmingham, a group of armed robbers drive a truck into a jewellery shop, stealing £300,000 worth of gold. They escape in less than 60 seconds. Forensic scene investigator Drew Birtles is dispatched to the jewellery shop to recover any forensic clues which could help identify the robbers. The investigation becomes more challenging when no real forensic evidence is found at the crime scene and the robbers switch cars - leaving the trail to go cold. Suspects are identified, and investigators hope that forensic evidence from the cars could provide the vital information needed to help solve the case and bring down the thieves.

programme.title: Nightmare Next Door
programme.desc: True crime documentary series. In these close-knitted communities, horrific murders have occurred, shaking them to the core. Every episode tells the story of a gruesome murder that happened in a small town. Delve into the heart of the cases through interviews with investigators, family members, prosecutors and neighbours. Various twists and turns can make you question reality, and the final outcome can surprise everyone involved. How well do you know the people next door?

programme.title: Homicide for the Holidays
programme.desc: A mother is brutally shot to death while driving her sons home from a Thanksgiving celebration. When the hunt for her killer leads to an unlikely suspect, investigators soon realize her murder is not as random as it once seemed.

programme.title: Homicide for the Holidays
programme.desc: The winter holidays are supposed to be a time where family and friends come together to celebrate all that is good in the world, but of course, there is a darker side to everything. This true-crime documentary series examines heinous murders committed by individuals during the holidays, where emotions have erupted and caused someone to commit the most deplorable of crimes. Each episode chronicles a different murder and its subsequent investigation.

programme.title: Two and a Half Men

programme.title: Married ... with Children
programme.desc: American comedy series. Al Bundy (Ed O'Neill) was once a promising young high school American football player. Now he is a middle-aged and cynical shoe salesman living in the suburbs of Chicago. After a long day working in his unfulfilling job, he goes home to a family who irritate and disrespect him. His wife Peggy (Katey Sagal) is a lazy woman who spends the families money on herself and openly mocks and taunts Al. Their two children are Kelly and Bud. Kelly, the eldest daughter is not a bright kid. She dates a string of guys much to the annoyance of her father. Her younger brother Bud is a smart boy, but he's not what he would like to be - a hit with the ladies. Starring Christina Applegate as Kelly and David Faustino as Bud.

programme.title: Mom
programme.desc: American sitcom about Christy, a single mother-of-two in recovery. Even after years of being sober, she is struggling with her addictions. She tries to stay positive but she is pushed to her limits when her mother, also a recovering alcoholic, returns back into her life. Together, this troubled daughter/mother duo try to rebuild their relationship and support each other to stay clean. The quarrels with her boss, teenage daughter and ex-husband do not make Christy's life any easier either. This comedy series deals not only with issues of addiction but a number of important topics in society including teen pregnancy, homelessness, domestic violence and death. Starring Anna Faris and Allison Janney as Christy and Bonnie Plunkett.

programme.title: Young Sheldon
programme.desc: For 11-year-old Sheldon Cooper, it isn't easy growing up in East Texas. Being a once-in-a-generation mind capable of advanced mathematics and science isn't always helpful in a land where church and football are king. And while the vulnerable, gifted and somewhat naïve Sheldon deals with the world, his very normal family must find a way to deal with him. His father, George, is struggling to find his way as a high school football coach and as father to a boy he doesn't understand. Sheldon's mother, Mary, fiercely protects and nurtures her son in a town where he just doesn't fit in. Sheldon's older brother, Georgie, does the best he can in high school, but it's tough to be cool when you're in the same classes with your odd 11-year-old brother. Finally, there's Sheldon's twin sister, Missy, who sometimes resents all the attention Sheldon gets, but also remains the one person who can reliably tell Sheldon the truth.

programme.title: Modern Family
programme.desc: The focus is on three families who are related: Jay and his young wife Gloria, with their son Manny. Claire, the daughter of Jay from a previous marriage, and her family; husband, Phil, and children, Hayley, Alex, and Luke. Then the third family, which compromises of Mitchell, Jay's other son and Claire's brother, and his family; Cameron, his husband, and their adopted child, Lily. All members of this diverse family have their own character quirks, which combine to create hilarious scenarios around family life. The show first aired in 2009, and has watched the characters grow through the years, addressing all the dramas that come with this. It does so in a light-hearted humorous way, with some heart-touching moments along the way. The series has won multiple awards, including "Outstanding Comedy Series" in 2014.

programme.title: Modern Family
programme.desc: Christmas is in full swing at the Dunphy house, until the kids get into trouble and Phil and Claire threaten to take away Christmas until one of them fesses up. Jay struggles with wanting to stick to his holiday traditions, while Gloria and Manny want to incorporate some of their Colombian practices, and Mitchell and Cameron take Lily to the mall for her first picture with Santa - but end up with a disgruntled Santa on their hands.

programme.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
programme.desc: Brand new series: In the final episode of series one, Peralta suspects a civic leader of money laundering but his investigation is shut down by the police commissioner. Determined to crack the case, he enlists Santiago and Captain Holt to help uncover more evidence, but risks suspension as a result. Boyle is devastated when Vivian ends their relationship, so his colleagues try to cheer him up.

programme.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
programme.desc: Brand new series: Season two of the US comedy about a group of New York City police detectives, starring Andy Samberg and Andre Braugher. In the first episode, Peralta's undercover FBI operation ends in a successful mass arrest but when he learns that one mobster has escaped, he enlists Boyle's help to track down the missing criminal. Captain Holt tests the squad's patience with practice drills in which Sergeant Jeffords plays different roles, and Gina pleads with Boyle to keep a secret.

programme.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
programme.desc: Brand new series: Captain Holt is taken by surprise when his long-time nemesis, Deputy Chief Madeline Wuntch (guest star Kyra Sedgwick), arrives to carry out an inspection of his precinct. Peralta and Jeffords test the boundaries between "work friendship" and "real friendship" while they investigate a stabbing at a trendy milk bar. Boyle searches for a "plus one" to take to his ex-wife's engagement party - can Diaz come to the rescue?

programme.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
programme.desc: Jake Peralta is Brooklyn's 99th precinct's best detective. The only mystery he hasn't solved, is how to grow up. When captain Holt is assigned as the precinct's new captain, Jake greets him with resistance, but after learning the challenges Holt has faced to get where he is today, the two begin to bond. Along with Amy Santiago, Rosa Diaz, Charles Boyle, Terry Jeffords, and the rest of the precinct, Jake solves crimes of the city, pursues criminal masterminds like the Pontiac bandit and tackles the hurdles of life in New York.

programme.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
programme.desc: US sitcom about a group of New York City police detectives. Peralta and Holt repeat their Halloween wager of the previous year as Peralta bets the Captain that he can steal his wristwatch before midnight, enlisting criminal assistance to achieve his goal. When Gina can't keep up with her college course, full-time job and dance rehearsals, she is kicked out of her dance team and reprimanded by Jeffords for a lack of commitment at work.

programme.title: Married ... with Children
programme.desc: American comedy series. Al Bundy (Ed O'Neill) was once a promising young high school American football player. Now he is a middle-aged and cynical shoe salesman living in the suburbs of Chicago. After a long day working in his unfulfilling job, he goes home to a family who irritate and disrespect him. His wife Peggy (Katey Sagal) is a lazy woman who spends the families money on herself and openly mocks and taunts Al. Their two children are Kelly and Bud. Kelly, the eldest daughter is not a bright kid. She dates a string of guys much to the annoyance of her father. Her younger brother Bud is a smart boy, but he's not what he would like to be - a hit with the ladies. Starring Christina Applegate as Kelly and David Faustino as Bud.

programme.title: Mom
programme.desc: American sitcom about Christy, a single mother-of-two in recovery. Even after years of being sober, she is struggling with her addictions. She tries to stay positive but she is pushed to her limits when her mother, also a recovering alcoholic, returns back into her life. Together, this troubled daughter/mother duo try to rebuild their relationship and support each other to stay clean. The quarrels with her boss, teenage daughter and ex-husband do not make Christy's life any easier either. This comedy series deals not only with issues of addiction but a number of important topics in society including teen pregnancy, homelessness, domestic violence and death. Starring Anna Faris and Allison Janney as Christy and Bonnie Plunkett.

Now he is a middle-aged and cynical shoe salesman living in the suburbs of Chicago. After a long day working in his unfulfilling job, he goes home to a family who irritate and disrespect him. His wife Peggy (Katey Sagal) is a lazy woman who spends the families money on herself and openly mocks and taunts Al. Their two children are Kelly and Bud. Kelly, the eldest daughter is not a bright kid. She dates a string of guys much to the annoyance of her father. Her younger brother Bud is a smart boy, but he's not what he would like to be - a hit with the ladies. Starring Christina Applegate as Kelly and David Faustino as Bud.

programme.title: Two and a Half Men
programme.desc: After his divorce, Alan Harper, a struggling chiropractor, moves in with his brother Charlie Harper, a womanizer and successful jingle writer as Charlie "temporarily" allows him and his son Jake, a food-obsessed, lazy kid to join him in his luxurious beach-house complicating Charlie's carefree life. Compulsively neat and control-freak Alan, hedonistic free spirited bachelor Charlie, Jake and other peculiar characters - Evelyn, their vain mother, Charlie's outspoken cleaning lady Berta and his rich, self-confessed stalker neighbor Rose soon get themselves into an abundance of crazy and hilarious situations.

programme.title: Friends
programme.desc: Delve into the hearts and minds of six friends living in New York City as they explore the anxieties and absurdities of true adulthood. This smart, sophisticated series offers a hilarious take on dating and working in the big city. As Rachel, Monica, Phoebe, Joey, Chandler and Ross realize, the search for happiness often seems to turn up more questions than answers. But while they look within for fulfillment, they also look out for one another during this exciting time when everything seems possible – as long as they've got Friends.

programme.title: Young Sheldon
programme.desc: For 11-year-old Sheldon Cooper, it isn't easy growing up in East Texas. Being a once-in-a-generation mind capable of advanced mathematics and science isn't always helpful in a land where church and football are king. And while the vulnerable, gifted and somewhat naïve Sheldon deals with the world, his very normal family must find a way to deal with him. His father, George, is struggling to find his way as a high school football coach and as father to a boy he doesn't understand. Sheldon's mother, Mary, fiercely protects and nurtures her son in a town where he just doesn't fit in. Sheldon's older brother, Georgie, does the best he can in high school, but it's tough to be cool when you're in the same classes with your odd 11-year-old brother. Finally, there's Sheldon's twin sister, Missy, who sometimes resents all the attention Sheldon gets, but also remains the one person who can reliably tell Sheldon the truth.

programme.title: Modern Family
programme.desc: The focus is on three families who are related: Jay and his young wife Gloria, with their son Manny. Claire, the daughter of Jay from a previous marriage, and her family; husband, Phil, and children, Hayley, Alex, and Luke. Then the third family, which compromises of Mitchell, Jay's other son and Claire's brother, and his family; Cameron, his husband, and their adopted child, Lily. All members of this diverse family have their own character quirks, which combine to create hilarious scenarios around family life. The show first aired in 2009, and has watched the characters grow through the years, addressing all the dramas that come with this. It does so in a light-hearted humorous way, with some heart-touching moments along the way. The series has won multiple awards, including "Outstanding Comedy Series" in 2014.

programme.title: Young Sheldon
programme.desc: For 11-year-old Sheldon Cooper, it isn't easy growing up in East Texas. Being a once-in-a-generation mind capable of advanced mathematics and science isn't always helpful in a land where church and football are king. And while the vulnerable, gifted and somewhat naïve Sheldon deals with the world, his very normal family must find a way to deal with him. His father, George, is struggling to find his way as a high school football coach and as father to a boy he doesn't understand. Sheldon's mother, Mary, fiercely protects and nurtures her son in a town where he just doesn't fit in. Sheldon's older brother, Georgie, does the best he can in high school, but it's tough to be cool when you're in the same classes with your odd 11-year-old brother. Finally, there's Sheldon's twin sister, Missy, who sometimes resents all the attention Sheldon gets, but also remains the one person who can reliably tell Sheldon the truth.

programme.title: Modern Family
programme.desc: The focus is on three families who are related: Jay and his young wife Gloria, with their son Manny. Claire, the daughter of Jay from a previous marriage, and her family; husband, Phil, and children, Hayley, Alex, and Luke. Then the third family, which compromises of Mitchell, Jay's other son and Claire's brother, and his family; Cameron, his husband, and their adopted child, Lily. All members of this diverse family have their own character quirks, which combine to create hilarious scenarios around family life. The show first aired in 2009, and has watched the characters grow through the years, addressing all the dramas that come with this. It does so in a light-hearted humorous way, with some heart-touching moments along the way. The series has won multiple awards, including "Outstanding Comedy Series" in 2014.

programme.desc: Homage is paid to Hitchcock's Strangers On A Train, in which two men agree to commit a murder for each other, as they have no connection to the victim. programme.title: Inspector George Gently
programme.desc: Detective drama. It is 1968 and the shame of illegitimacy still burns the cheeks of single mothers and the families who force their unmarried daughters into 'mother and baby homes'. When the adopted child of a middle-class couple is kidnapped, suspicion falls upon the baby's birth mother. However, Gently and Bacchus's investigation into the mother and baby home itself reveals a much darker side to this hothouse of morality, and raises serious questions about this seemingly perfect couple.

programme.title: All Creatures Great and Small
programme.desc: James is settling back into life at home but still needs to find his feet with baby Jimmy as he's not yet confident with babies. Helen leaves father and son alone for the day to go up to Heston and realises how much Jenny has grown up in recent months, now best friends with newly arrived land girl, Doris. Meanwhile, Mrs Hall is caught in the middle of Siegfried and her new boss, Mr Bosworth as they fall out over some of Mr Bosworth's safety tactics. Baby Jimmy joins James and Carmody on their veterinary round and charms the farmers. James does a good job juggling work and parenting until he gets distracted at Dowson's farm. Jenny tells Helen that she's not been up at the farm much since Jimmy was born but when Jenny decides to ignore Helen's advice and take their horses out, there are significant consequences. Helen and Jenny talk through their issues and Helen realises she needs to allow Jenny to grow up, even if it means her exploring the wider world. Mrs Hall and Siegfried find a poisoned dog and try to work out how what's happened.

programme.title: Agatha Christie's Marple
programme.desc: When a murder is announced in the personal columns of the Chipping Cleghorn Gazette, the locals wonder if it is just a game. The curious villagers then assemble at Lettie Blacklock's house to find that their host did not place the advert; the room goes dark and three gun shots ring out. Lettie is injured in the process, but the man who fired the gun ends up dead. Miss Marple pays a visit to her friend Amy Murgatroyd and sets about uncovering the dark secrets of Chipping Cleghorn.

programme.title: All Creatures Great and Small
programme.desc: British drama series set in the 1930s, centering on the eccentric veterinarian Siegfried Farnon and his colleagues, James Herriot, and Tristan, Siegried's younger brother. Working out of the stunning Skeldale House in the Yorkshire Dales , the trio of companions endeavour themselves to the surrounding community by providing a valuable service to the region's animals. Adapted from If Only They Could Talk by James Herriot (Alf Wight's pen name), the delightful series is a celebration of the wonderful stories penned by Wight, bringing to life the iconic characters from his much-loved books.

programme.title: All Creatures Great and Small
programme.desc: It's Christmas Eve, and the day before Helen and Hugh's much anticipated wedding. James is trying to bury his pain over Helen and has invited his new girlfriend Connie to the annual Skeldale Christmas party. Preparations are well under way: Tristan has decked the halls with mistletoe, while Mrs Hall has laid on a feast and is looking forward to her son Edward returning for Christmas. Siegfried is delighted when Dorothy turns up and wonders if now is the time to throw caution to the wind. As the house fills with locals, James receives a call from Bert Chapman, who wants help with his dog who is struggling to give birth. James has to leave the party and is surprised when Helen asks if she can go with him to get away from all the wedding gossip. Up at the Chapman's, James is faced with a puppy stuck in the birth canal, offering Helen a chance to witness just how much he loves being a vet. When it's time to leave, James is horrified to discover the fog has descended, trapping them high up in the Dales until morning. James calls Skeldale and promises to get Helen back to Darrowby in time for the wedding, all the time wondering if he will be able to suppress his true feelings for her.

programme.title: All Creatures Great and Small
programme.desc: It's spring in 1938, and James's parents are overjoyed when he's offered a position at his old mentor's forward-thinking practice in Glasgow. When he returns to the Dales, James is reminded of how much he loves the place and the people - and thinks of one person who it would be worth staying in the Dales for. Since Helen Alderson left Hugh Hulton at the altar, she has kept a low profile and James has given her the space she needed. But the pair find themselves forced together again when neighbouring farmer Rob Benson's sheep are in trouble. Inspired by his time at the Glasgow surgery, James pushes Siegfried to let Tristan do more veterinary jobs so that they can take on more small animal cases at Skeldale House. Tristan tends to a budgerigar whilst Mrs Hall uncovers a difficult truth.

programme.title: All Creatures Great and Small

programme.title: All Creatures Great and Small
programme.desc: The fate of a struggling young widow causes difficulties for James and Helen's burgeoning romance. Meanwhile, Siegfried has another scheme to whip Tristan into shape, and a visit from Tricki Woo causes chaos in Skeldale House. James is called out to visit widow Phyllis Dalby and finds that her young herd of cows are seriously ill — which could leave her family with nothing. James struggles to accept that perhaps there is nothing he can do to save them, and therefore her farm. A reminder from Phyllis on how fleeting time can be pushes James to take a risk with Helen, but his dilemma causes friction between the pair. Siegfried can't abide Tristan not having enough to do and so presents him with a new challenge. Tristan's need to impress his older brother makes him feel like he needs to produce results at any cost, but James reminds him that honesty is often the best policy. Tricki Woo turns up needing a babysitter and Mrs Pumphrey returns.

programme.title: Grantchester
programme.desc: Grantchester is a British detective drama, set in the 1950s Cambridgeshire village of the same name. It features first Anglican vicar Sidney Chambers and his successor Reverend Will Davenport, who join their forces with the overworked Detective Inspector Geordie Keating in order investigate a series of mysterious terrifying crimes in their once-peaceful village. Sidney is in love with Amanda Kendall, but she is planning to marry someone else.

programme.title: Grantchester
programme.desc: With Violet gone, Sidney loses himself in drink. After a heavy whiskey session leaves him without his jacket, and little memory of the night before, Sidney discovers to his horror that he was the last person to see a young woman alive. As he struggles to remember her final words, Geordie grows concerned – both for the murdered girl, so callously abandoned outside a local slum, and for his friend's troubled state of mind. At the slum, Sidney and Geordie identify the girl as Sadie Parker, and meet her shocked roommates Ava, Lottie and Peggy. Although they claim to be seamstresses, Geordie realises they're involved in a life of vice. Sidney finds his missing jacket in Sadie's room, realising he gave it to her the night before. They track down the owner and employer of the girls, Mr Simpson, who is playing golf with councilman Archer Davis. Sidney's frustration with his own failings bubbles over into an angry confrontation with Simpson. As Geordie's investigation leads him to Simpson's nightclub, Sidney attempts to atone for his failings – and both men, in their own way, begin to help the downtrodden women of the slum find their voice.

programme.title: Agatha Christie's Marple
programme.desc: When a murder is announced in the personal columns of the Chipping Cleghorn Gazette, the locals wonder if it is just a game. The curious villagers then assemble at Lettie Blacklock's house to find that their host did not place the advert; the room goes dark and three gun shots ring out. Lettie is injured in the process, but the man who fired the gun ends up dead. Miss Marple pays a visit to her friend Amy Murgatroyd and sets about uncovering the dark secrets of Chipping Cleghorn.

programme.title: Agatha Christie's Marple
programme.desc: Miss Marple is asked to help Gwenda Halliday, a wealthy young woman who has bought a house on the English coast, only to experience disturbing visions. Soon Gwenda discovers that, instead of spending all her life in India, she had lived in the house as a child. The visions are actually flashes of memory - and she realizes she witnessed the murder of a beautiful woman who was a singer for an acting troupe known as The Funnybones.

programme.title: Murdoch Mysteries
programme.desc: Murdoch Mysteries is a fine example of canadian detective series. The main character is William Murdoch, a talented police detective working in Toronto, Ontario in the late 19th century. He uses methods of forensic science to solve the mysterious murder cases and these methods are ahead of his time. His motto is "Nothing is impossible" and his confidence and determination help him to cope with the most complicated tasks that are beyond the scope of other detectives. William is not alone in his investigations, his superior, inspector Brackenreid, Doctor Julia Ogden, expert skilled in pathology and the inexperienced but enthusiastic assistant Constable George Crabtree are by his side. Sometimes real historical figures appear in the series, such as Jack London, William Churchill, Nikola Tesla etc.

programme.title: Inspector George Gently
programme.desc: Detective drama. It is 1968 and the shame of illegitimacy still burns the cheeks of single mothers and the families who force their unmarried daughters into 'mother and baby homes'. When the adopted child of a middle-class couple is kidnapped, suspicion falls upon the baby's birth mother. However, Gently and Bacchus's investigation into the mother and baby home itself reveals a much darker side to this hothouse of morality, and raises serious questions about this seemingly perfect couple.

programme.title: All Creatures Great and Small
programme.desc: James is settling back into life at home but still needs to find his feet with baby Jimmy as he's not yet confident with babies. Helen leaves father and son alone for the day to go up to Heston and realises how much Jenny has grown up in recent months, now best friends with newly arrived land girl, Doris. Meanwhile, Mrs Hall is caught in the middle of Siegfried and her new boss, Mr Bosworth as they fall out over some of Mr Bosworth's safety tactics. Baby Jimmy joins James and Carmody on their veterinary round and charms the farmers. James does a good job juggling work and parenting until he gets distracted at Dowson's farm. Jenny tells Helen that she's not been up at the farm much since Jimmy was born but when Jenny decides to ignore Helen's advice and take their horses out, there are significant consequences. Helen and Jenny talk through their issues and Helen realises she needs to allow Jenny to grow up, even if it means her exploring the wider world. Mrs Hall and Siegfried find a poisoned dog and try to work out how what's happened.

programme.title: Agatha Christie's Marple
programme.desc: When a murder is announced in the personal columns of the Chipping Cleghorn Gazette, the locals wonder if it is just a game. The curious villagers then assemble at Lettie Blacklock's house to find that their host did not place the advert; the room goes dark and three gun shots ring out. Lettie is injured in the process, but the man who fired the gun ends up dead. Miss Marple pays a visit to her friend Amy Murgatroyd and sets about uncovering the dark secrets of Chipping Cleghorn.

programme.title: All Creatures Great and Small
programme.desc: British drama series set in the 1930s, centering on the eccentric veterinarian Siegfried Farnon and his colleagues, James Herriot, and Tristan, Siegried's younger brother. Working out of the stunning Skeldale House in the Yorkshire Dales , the trio of companions endeavour themselves to the surrounding community by providing a valuable service to the region's animals. Adapted from If Only They Could Talk by James Herriot (Alf Wight's pen name), the delightful series is a celebration of the wonderful stories penned by Wight, bringing to life the iconic characters from his much-loved books.

programme.title: All Creatures Great and Small
programme.desc: It's Christmas Eve, and the day before Helen and Hugh's much anticipated wedding. James is trying to bury his pain over Helen and has invited his new girlfriend Connie to the annual Skeldale Christmas party. Preparations are well under way: Tristan has decked the halls with mistletoe, while Mrs Hall has laid on a feast and is looking forward to her son Edward returning for Christmas. Siegfried is delighted when Dorothy turns up and wonders if now is the time to throw caution to the wind. As the house fills with locals, James receives a call from Bert Chapman, who wants help with his dog who is struggling to give birth. James has to leave the party and is surprised when Helen asks if she can go with him to get away from all the wedding gossip. Up at the Chapman's, James is faced with a puppy stuck in the birth canal, offering Helen a chance to witness just how much he loves being a vet. When it's time to leave, James is horrified to discover the fog has descended, trapping them high up in the Dales until morning. James calls Skeldale and promises to get Helen back to Darrowby in time for the wedding, all the time wondering if he will be able to suppress his true feelings for her.

programme.title: All Creatures Great and Small
programme.desc: It's spring in 1938, and James's parents are overjoyed when he's offered a position at his old mentor's forward-thinking practice in Glasgow. When he returns to the Dales, James is reminded of how much he loves the place and the people - and thinks of one person who it would be worth staying in the Dales for. Since Helen Alderson left Hugh Hulton at the altar, she has kept a low profile and James has given her the space she needed. But the pair find themselves forced together again when neighbouring farmer Rob Benson's sheep are in trouble. Inspired by his time at the Glasgow surgery, James pushes Siegfried to let Tristan do more veterinary jobs so that they can take on more small animal cases at Skeldale House. Tristan tends to a budgerigar whilst Mrs Hall uncovers a difficult truth.

programme.title: All Creatures Great and Small

programme.title: All Creatures Great and Small
programme.desc: The fate of a struggling young widow causes difficulties for James and Helen's burgeoning romance. Meanwhile, Siegfried has another scheme to whip Tristan into shape, and a visit from Tricki Woo causes chaos in Skeldale House. James is called out to visit widow Phyllis Dalby and finds that her young herd of cows are seriously ill — which could leave her family with nothing. James struggles to accept that perhaps there is nothing he can do to save them, and therefore her farm. A reminder from Phyllis on how fleeting time can be pushes James to take a risk with Helen, but his dilemma causes friction between the pair. Siegfried can't abide Tristan not having enough to do and so presents him with a new challenge. Tristan's need to impress his older brother makes him feel like he needs to produce results at any cost, but James reminds him that honesty is often the best policy. Tricki Woo turns up needing a babysitter and Mrs Pumphrey returns.

programme.title: Grantchester
programme.desc: Grantchester is a British detective drama, set in the 1950s Cambridgeshire village of the same name. It features first Anglican vicar Sidney Chambers and his successor Reverend Will Davenport, who join their forces with the overworked Detective Inspector Geordie Keating in order investigate a series of mysterious terrifying crimes in their once-peaceful village. Sidney is in love with Amanda Kendall, but she is planning to marry someone else.

programme.title: Kosmo
programme.desc: Koer Kosmo on Williamsite pere suur karvane lemmikloom. Tema ja 13-aastane Robi on südamesõbrad, ent ühel päeval juhtub õnnetus - Kosmo jääb auto alla ning saab tõsiselt vigastada. Robil ja tema parimal sõbral, nutikal ratastoolitüdrukul Elisel õnnestub robootikafirmas, kus töötab Robi ema, asendada Kosmo vigastatud organid bioonilistega, ja sel viisil koera elu päästa. Bioonilised kehaosad annavad Kosmole supervõimed, tänu neile võimetele aitab Kosmo Robil ja Elisel lahendada kõiksugu põnevaid saladusi ning tuua päevavalgele kurikaelte salasepitsusi Merisilma linnakeses, kus nad kõik elavad. Sündmustele lisab põnevust asjaolu, et lapsed peavad kiivalt varjama oma koera saladust, sest selle ilmsikstulek võib maksta Robi emale töökoha. Ema Ester on aga ainuke, kes perele leiva lauale toob.

programme.title: Muumioru lood
programme.desc: Muumitroll otsustab talveunest loobuda ja seada sammud salapärase Üksiku mäe poole, et leida üles Nuuskmõmmik. Üksindust ihkav Nuuskmõmmik on aga sõbra kohale ilmumisest häiritud ja Muumitroll kiirustab koju tagasi, jäädes lumetormi kätte.

programme.title: Swang
programme.desc: 10-osaline sari visadusest ja unistustest, mis võivad täituda. 12-aastane Lumi ja tema sõbranna Lelle soovivad suvevaheajal saada rolli muusikalis "Swang". Lumile meeldib tegeleda muusikaga ja laulda, Lelle aga armastab tantsida. Algab suvi täis teatrit, muusikat ja uute sõprade leidmist. Koos seisavad noored silmitsi väljakutsete, põnevuse ja armumistega. Pärast seda suve ei ole miski enam endine.

programme.title: Jakob, Mimmi ja rääkivad koerad
programme.desc: Jakob on linnalaps, kes unistab isa eeskujul arhitektiametist. Kui isa on tööl, veedab poiss aega maju joonistades ja niisama unistades. Ühel päeval sõidab isa pikemale tööreisile ning Jakob peab veetma terve nädala oma kange iseloomuga nõo Mimmi ning tolle endisest piraadist isa juures. Ootamatult selgub, et Mimmi naabruskonna parki tahetakse maha võtta, et sinna asemele pilvelõhkujad ehitada. Jakob ja Mimmi otsustavad üheskoos selle vastu võitlema hakata. Siis aga ilmneb, et nad vajavad kohalike koerte abi. Ja need koerad oskavad rääkida! "Jakob, Mimmi ja rääkivad koerad" on Läti-Poola animatsioon, mis võlub nii oma loojutustamise kui pildikeelega. Filmi autoriks on Edmunds Jansons, kes lõpetanud Priit Pärna käe all Eesti Kunstiakadeemia ning kogunud kodumaal tuntust lisaks lühifilmidele ka raamatuillustraatori ja graafilise disainerina.

programme.title: Kahevõistluse MK-etapp Schonachis
programme.desc: Kahevõistluse MK-sari jätkub neljanädalase pausi järel Saksamaal, kus muu maailma paremate kõrval asub taas stardijoonele ka Kristjan Ilves. Laupäevase võistluspäeva Schonachis avab hüppevoor normaalmäelt.

programme.title: Vahemeri
programme.desc: Matriarhi juhitud karjades elavad emased kašelotid aitavad üksteisel poegi kasvatada, aga nende suhtlemist segab inimeste tekitatud mürareostus. Emased kaheksajalad on järglaste nimel kõigeks valmis ja pärast munade koorumist nad hukkuvad. Äsja koorunud merikilpkonnad teevad esimesi samme ohtlikul Kreeka rannal ja üht viimast Vahemerel pesitsevat merikotkapaari tabab kohutav õnnetus.

programme.title: Betty diagnoosid
programme.desc: Täna on Talula suurpäev, ta saab endale patsiendi ja loodab, et tegemist pole pelgalt gripiga. Tema rõõmuks ongi patsiendil haruldase troopilise haiguse sümptomid. Karla ilmub uuesti haiglasse ja jätab Tamási tütre Lilli õdede tuppa.

programme.title: Betty diagnoosid
programme.desc: Tamás on koidikul koos Lilliga Lizzy, Talula ja Betty ukse taga, laps on haige ja mees ei jaksa enam. Betty laseb end ümber veenda ning hoolitseb vabal päeval beebi ja Tamási eest. Lizzy peab sõbra äraolekul vahetuse juhtimise üle võtma.

programme.title: Betty diagnoosid
programme.desc: Betty ärkab Tamási voodis. Noorel isal ei saakski enam paremini minna: tal on tütreke ja unistuste naine. Betty aga pole sugugi nii rahul ja tal on hea meel, et töö mõtted mujale viib. Lizzy käitub imelikult.

programme.title: Betty diagnoosid
programme.desc: Tänane patsient Marvin Leistner on Betty ja tema kolleegide jaoks vana tuttav. Kuid seekord on poisiga lood teisiti. Betty püüab Marvinit hoopis teistmoodi aidata. Samuti on Betty ema hädas.

programme.title: Teekond Hispaania
programme.desc: Tuglas tegi teoks Eesti kunstnike Pariisi kogukonna unistuse. Nii Aleksander Tassa kui ka Konrad Mägi igatsesid vahetpidamata Hispaaniasse pääseda, et tutvuda sealse eksootilise loodusega, süüa apelsine puu otsast, näha härjavõitlust ja kõike seda, mida olid kuulnud. Kunagi polnud neil aga selleks piisavalt raha. Tuglasest sai Eesti reisikirjanduse teerajaja. Konrad Mäele andis Tuglas võimaluse valada oma lõunamaaigatsus reisikirja illustratsioonidesse. Veider olukord - mees, kes pole kunagi Hispaanias käinud, loob reisikirjale pilte. Teises osas peatub Tuglas pikemalt Sevillas. "Oo, kui ilus on Sevilla," õhkab kunstnik oma reisikirjas korduvalt. Meiegi leiame oma teekonnal paar eestlast.

programme.title: Jänki jälgedes Hiiumaal
programme.desc: 1992. aastal maandus Hiiumaale UFO-mees Ameerikast - Douglas Wells. Rahukorpuse poolt Hiiumaa põllumajandust edendama kupatatud Wells õppis dünamiidiga kalapüüdmist, paadiga lammaste vedamist ja hiiu jonni asjade läbiviimisel. Ta laulis Eesti edetabelitesse enda kirjutatud loo "Kas te räägite inglise keelt?" ja õppis selgeks eesti keele. 15 aastat hiljem on saarel oma Eiffeli torn, metssigade kasvatus, Lastefestival ja palju muud, mida Douglas veel näinudki pole. Vanu jälgi otsides ja uutes kohtades käies selgus, et kõik on ikkagi sama - inimesed on endiselt ilusad ja head. Saatejuhid Kaidor Kahar ja Douglas Wells. Autor ja režissöör Elo Selirand, produtsent Maarek Toompere.

programme.title: Lendav klassiruum
programme.desc: Martina soovib pääseda Johann-Sigismundi internaatkooli maalilistes Aplides. Sisseastumise ajal tutvub ta südika Jo, heatahtliku Matze ja nutika Uliga ning satub rivaalitsevate klikkide keskele. Internaadi juhataja Justus Bökh plaanib ühise näidendi lavale toomisega osapooli lepitada, kuid kas see õnnestub?

programme.title: Buratino tegutseb jälle
programme.desc: Seekord tulevad sõbrad ideele meisterdada suslet - see on nagu puslemäng, aga siiski omamoodi. Kui hästi õnnestub, miks siis mitte teha kohe oma firma - susletehas, direktoriga ja puha. Kuid kui Buratino läheb suslesid naabritele müüma, saab ta ühe ukse taga kokku...

programme.title: Swang
programme.desc: 10-osaline sari visadusest ja unistustest, mis võivad täituda. 12-aastane Lumi ja tema sõbranna Lelle soovivad suvevaheajal saada rolli muusikalis "Swang". Lumile meeldib tegeleda muusikaga ja laulda, Lelle aga armastab tantsida. Algab suvi täis teatrit, muusikat ja uute sõprade leidmist. Koos seisavad noored silmitsi väljakutsete, põnevuse ja armumistega. Pärast seda suve ei ole miski enam endine.

programme.title: Mina ja Miia
programme.desc: Miia on Carinale abiks. Üks kohalik talunik, Hektor, tuleb nende juurde oma eesliga, kes olevat haige. Õnneks on Carinal olukorrale lahendus. Miia saab ennustuse, kus on mainitud kedagi "väikest ja roosat". Tsentoopiasse jõudes mõistab ta, et see saab olla ainult Kiaara.

programme.title: Aktuaalne kaamera (viipekeeles)
programme.desc: No description available

programme.title: Härra Septime'i restoran
programme.desc: Vana hea Prantsuse komöödia (1966), mille peaosas särab igihaljas koomik Louis de Funes. Härra Septime'i peenesse restorani Pariisis saabub õhtusöögile Lõuna-Ameerika riigipea, ent ühe roa plahvatuslikult efektse serveerimise järel haihtub ta kui tina tuhka. Oma ehmatuseks leiab restoraniomanik end korraga peamise kahtlusaluse rollist. Asjasse sekkuvad politsei, kõmureporterid ja põrandaalune terroriorganisatsioon ning kesk kogu seda möllu otsustab härra Septime kadunud presidendi omal käel üles otsida.

programme.title: Tallinn täis muusikat
programme.desc: Tallinn kannab UNESCO muusikalinna uhket tiitlit ja see annab muusikale linnaruumis erilise tähenduse. Kadri Voorand, Sissi Nylia Benita, Rasmus Puur, Kristjan Järvi, Andres Kõpper ja Sven Grünberg viivad meid pealinna märgilistesse paikadesse ning avavad oma inspiratsiooniallikad.

programme.title: Nii ta on
programme.desc: Vallo Toomla dokumentaalfilm viib vaataja Eesti väikekohtades elavate meeste maailma, näidates nende argipäevaseid rōōme ja muresid. Kuidas kasvatab oma nelja poega endine seakasvataja Janek ja millest unistab hooldekodu omanik Meelis? Kuidas metsamees Rein leiab eluvärskuse noolemängust ja talupidaja Eku kartulikülvist? Kas assenisaator Kaido kahetseb midagi ja kui tihti ta oma naisele lilli kingib? Kas ka hobileidur Juss näeb Jumalat pisiasjades ja milline ikkagi on hüdraulilise niiduki ülekanne? Need on pildid elu keskpaika jõudnud meeste elumõistmisest, eluga leppimisest ja elurõõmu otsingutest selle leppimise sees. Film on kui rahustav soe sõõm inimlikkust keset praegust keerukat ja raevukaid konflikte täis maailmas. Lihtsuses võib olla võlu.

programme.title: Andy Warhol. Elu kunstis
programme.desc: Andy Warhol oli säravaim tegelane Ameerika 20. sajandi kunstis. Ühest küljest mõistatuslik kuju, teisest küljest maailmakuulus kunstnik ja kultuse objekt. Andy Warhol oli ennekõike kaasaegse elu kroonik, kes defineeris uuesti kunsti olemuse. Tema kuulsus on kestnud kindlasti kauem kui 15 minutit.

programme.title: Agendid on igavesed
programme.desc: Taani Rahvusliku Sümfooniaorkestri esituses kõlab muusika populaarsetest spiooni- ja detektiivfilmidest nagu "Sherlock Holmes", "Võimatu missioon", "Roosa panter", "Teemandid on igavesed", "James Bond" ja paljud teised. Orkestrit juhatab Hans Ek, solist on Caroline Henderson.

programme.title: Kallima naeratus
programme.desc: Telelavastuse sisuks on noore vetelpäästja Aleksandri ja kena postiljoni Kristiina armastuslugu. Peaosades Liina Vahtrik ja Jan Uuspõld. Stsenarist ja lavastaja Valentin Kuik, helilooja Olav Ehala, toimetaja Hanneli Reili.

programme.title: Lendurid koduteel
programme.desc: Stsenaarist Priit Pärn, režissöörid Priit Pärn ja Olga Pärn. Eesti Joonisfilm. Lendurite kodutee on pikk ja ränk. Kõrbekuumus vaheldub mägede jäise tuulega, mudamülgaste ja moskiitodega. Sellised on nende päevad, täis sihipärast lootusetust. Kuid iga päeva järel saabub öö .

programme.title: ERR.ee uudised
programme.desc: Eesti Rahvusringhäälingu uudised - Eesti ja kogu maailma kõige värskemad uudised.

programme.title: ERR.ee uudised
programme.desc: Eesti Rahvusringhäälingu uudised - Eesti ja kogu maailma kõige värskemad uudised.

programme.title: Osoon
programme.desc: Looduskaitsja Mati Sepp on võtnud südameasjaks tuvastada rikkumisi Eesti metsades tehtavatel töödel ja teavitada nendest Keskkonnaametit. Vaatame koos Matiga kriitilise pilguga ringi Lahemaa metsades ja uurime, kui hooliv ja seaduskuulekas on meie metsamajandamise kultuur täna. Taanlane Henrik Truelsen on tõeline leiutaja, kes on välja töötanud vastupidava, kuid kompostitava plasti alternatiivi. Vetikatest valmistatud plastilaadne materjal valmib tema enda koduses "tööstuses". Milline võiks olla selle tulevikupotentsiaal ja kasulikkus keskkonnale? Saate autorid on Kristo Elias ja Sander Loite, toimetaja Marit Valk, režissöör Keiti Väliste, produtsent Heiki Sepp.

programme.title: Töörööbikud
programme.desc: Kas sinu töö pakub sulle pinget? Elektrimontaažilukksepp Maigi ja kõrgepingeliinide ehituse projektijuht Kaspar võivad sellele küsimusele kindlasti jaatavalt vastata, sest nende tööpäevad on otsast otsani särtsu täis. Režissöör Märten Vaher, autor-toimetaja Marit Ummelas, produtsent Hannela Lippus.

programme.title: Heureka
programme.desc: Leib on meie toidulaual väga tähtis toiduaine, kuid kui tihti sa mõtled sellele, kuidas see poodi jõuab? Seda pätsi leiba või saia, mille sa poes korvi paned, hakatakse leivatehases valmistama juba eelmisel päeval. Kuid see ei tähenda, et sa saaksid vana leiva, vaid selle valmimisprotsess on nii pikk. Vaatame, kuidas leivad ja saiad valmivad ning lisaks saad ka nippe ise leiva küpsetamisega katsetamiseks. Tootja Downtown Pictures OÜ.

programme.title: Lahutus Eesti moodi
programme.desc: Ettevõtjast Laura (Liina Vahtrik) tahab lahutada üle 20 aasta kestnud abielu oma muusikaõpetajana töötavast mehest Akslist (Jan Uuspõld), sest nad on totaalselt lahku kasvanud. Mees on vinguv konservatiiv, naine aga kunstnikuhingega liberaal. Kõik nende tõekspidamised on justkui vastandid, nad ei leia enam pisemateski asjades ühist keelt. Laura ja Aksel lähevad suhtenõustaja juurde, kes koostab neile kümnest ülesandest koosneva humaanse lahutusplaani. Esimeses osas peavad Laura ja Aksel taaslooma oma kõige esimese kohtumise. Naljakasse tegevusse sekkuvad nii poeg kui ka tütar ja samuti pöörased naabrid Tauno (Ago Anderson) ning Mirjam (Marilyn Jurman). Stsenarist Martin Algus, režissöör Ergo Kuld.

programme.title: Aeg õppida
programme.desc: Mõned tunnevad enda eriala ära juba noorena, teised satuvad aga õige asja peale hiljem. Edukaks võib saada mõlemal juhul, sest õppida on võimalik igas vanuses. Oksana oli 39-aastane, kui otsustas minna keskkooli. Kuus aastat hiljem õpib ta ikka veel - kutsekool seljataga, omandab Oksana täna müügikorralduses rakenduslikku kõrgharidust. Mihkel aga leidis juba poisikesena selle, mis teda kõnetas - mehhatroonika. Ta võttis kindla suuna minna õppima tehnikaülikooli. Nüüd töötab ta tootetehnoloogia juhina suurettevõttes ja loob innovaatilisi tooteid kahes väikses startupis. Selles valdkonnas viib suurte tegudeni pidev õppimine. Režissöör Andres Lepasar, toimetaja Mari Tamm, produtsent Lii Kuldmäe.

programme.title: Õnne 13
programme.desc: Iiris tutvustab lõpuks Ainole oma uut kallimat Siimu. Evelin ja Henry kutsuvad Margiti oma hooldusõiguse jagamise küsimust arutama. Tiina annab Margnale aru nende ühise äri käekäigu kohta. Torim küsib Rebekalt, kas ta siis varastas Filipilt kella või ei.

programme.title: Maahommik
programme.desc: "Maahommik" rändab mööda Eestimaad ringi ja kohtub erinevate inimeste ja nende põnevate tegemistega. Teie ees rullub lahti maaelu värvipalett koos kõikide oma varjunditega. Loomad, taimed, talud, tööd ja musttuhat muud lugu ootab teid just "Maahommiku" saates. Saatejuht on Kerli Dello. Vastutav toimetaja Maili Metssalu, režissöörid Mikk Mäe ja Mati Kark, produtsent Tiina-Mari Koljak.

programme.title: Segasummasuvila ratastel
programme.desc: Kuigi teekond jätkub läbi riikide, kus juba varem käidud, siis seekordse sõidu on perekond planeerinud pisut teistmoodi, et avastada põnevaid mänguplatse ja näha Lätit, Leedut ning Poolat uuest küljest. Loomulikult on pereema Annil jagada nii mõnedki kavalad reisinipid ja ühtlasi tõstetakse pisut saladuseloori ka perekonna reisikulude osas. Üllatavaid majutuskohti jagub seltskonna teele omajagu ja nii võib õhtupimeduses hirmu tekitanud koht muunduda ööga lausa ahhetama panevaks õiteparadiisiks.

programme.title: Pealtnägija
programme.desc: "Pealtnägija" on Eesti pikima ajalooga ja teletabelite tipus olev uuriv ajakirjanduse saade, mis toob vaatajateni põnevad ja paljastavad lood meie ühiskonna telgitagustest. Lisaks teravatele uurimustele vahendab saade ka haaravaid persoone ja meeldejäävaid reportaaže sündmustest, mille pealtnägijaks tavaline inimene naljalt ei satu. Saatejuhid Mihkel Kärmas, Kristjan Pihl, Piia Osula, Taavi Eilat ja Margit Kilumets. Režissöörid Raivo Maripuu ja Vladlen Pobjaržin, produtsent Piret Priisaar.

programme.title: Kirjandusministri juures
programme.desc: Mart Juur viib läbi meeleolukad vestlused meie tuntud kirjanikega.

programme.title: Eesti lood
programme.desc: Film jälgib käputäit Eestis elavaid vene juurtega inimesi, kes on erinevalt paljudest oma kaasmaalastest leidnud tee eestlaste südamesse. Kas, mil moel ja kui palju on nad pidanud selle eest lõivu maksma või oma identiteedist ning grupisisestest väärtustest mööda libisema, muganduma? Kui palju on see sõltunud välimisest või sisemisest survest? Kellena nad ennast õigupoolest tunnevad, kuidas see muutub ja millest sõltub? Millised on nende suhted vanemate ja sõpradega, kellega võidu on tulnud toime tulla suurrahva esindajana vähemusgruppi kuulumise "traagilise" kogemusega? Režissöör Indrek Spungin, produtsent Anu Veermäe-Kaldra, operaator ja monteerija Sten-Johan Lill.

programme.title: Karen Pirie
programme.desc: Karen avastab omaaegses uurimises palju vastuolusid ja lohakust, mis viib teda aina lähemale uskumatule versioonile. Et aga tõeline süüdlane kinni võtta, läheb noorel uurijal vaja tohutut julgust ja meelekindlust.

programme.title: Kahevõistluse MK-etapp Schonachis
programme.desc: Kahevõistluse Schonachi MK-etapi esimene võitja selgub pärast 10 kilomeetri murdmaadistantsi. Ajavahed suusasõiduks said paika hommikuse hüppevooruga ja kõrgesse mängu soovib taaskord sekkuda ka Kristjan Ilves.

programme.title: Laskesuusatamise MK-etapp Ruhpoldingis
programme.desc: Laskesuusatamise MK-sari jätkub Baierimaa laskesuusamekas Ruhpoldingis. Ülekandeid kommenteerivad Tarmo Tiisler ja Margus Ader.

programme.title: Miks sa liigud?
programme.desc: "Miks sa liigud?" on lühidokumentaalfilm, mis uurib, kuidas kolm noort inimest defineerivad oma igapäevast liikumisvajadust. Neid noori seob loomulikku liikumist uuriv kogukond Movement Tallinn.

programme.title: Pöörane aasta
programme.desc: Aasta algus on maakeral poolusest pooluseni äärmuste aeg. Jäises Arktikas valitseb paukuv pakane ning Austraalia kõrbes võimutseb kõrvetav kuumus ja päike. Ekvatoriaalses Aafrikas muudavad aasta tugevaimad paduvihmad maastikku ja kogu elu oma teel.

programme.title: Tanel ja kanad
programme.desc: Heureka! Pärast aastaid kestnud raskusi kanalas saab Tanel viimaks selgust kõigi tema kanaprobleemide põhjustest. Äntu Mõisa kanakasvatajaga koos leitakse lahendused, mis peaks edaspidi tagama kanakarja parema tervise ja stabiilsema mahemunaäri. Aga niipea kui üks mure lahendatud, näitab ennast järgmine. Tanel on jäänud bürokraatia hammasrataste vahele ja teda ähvardab pisikese lohakusvea tõttu suurest PRIA mahetoetusest ilmajäämine. Peategelane Tanel Tang, režissöör Elisa Avik, toimetajad Liis Ilves ja Marit Valk, operaator Raido Pedak, produtsent Elisa Avik. Tootja Sync Media.

programme.title: Aktuaalne kaamera
programme.desc: "Aktuaalne kaamera" on Eesti Televisiooni igapäevane eestikeelne uudistesaade.

programme.title: Laske mind Lavale
programme.desc: Võistlussaate eelviimases osas ootab kuut julget noort Rakvere teater. Osalejad panevad end proovile lõbusas pantomiimiharjutuses ja peavad laval taas kord toime tulema ootamatu üllatusega. Kui hästi hakkab noorte hammas peale Shakespeare'i legendaarse "Macbethi" tekstile, hindavad žüriis Ülle Lichtfeldt, Tiina Mälberg ja Margus Grosnõi.

programme.title: Rakett 69
programme.desc: Rakett 69 pardal alustab teadusrännakut 12 andekat noort. Punase, rohelise ja sinise võistkonna omavaheline koostöö läbib esimese tuleproovi jalgpalliväljakul. Et mäng saaks alata, on vaja palli pinnalaotus õigetest kujunditest kokku panna. Kuna jalgpallimängu ei saa võita ilma väravat löömata, siis tuleb raketlastel ehitada löögimasin. Tootja Vesilind OÜ.

programme.title: Segasummasuvila ratastel
programme.desc: Suurel ja laial Saksamaal on Keskülladele palju pakkuda ja kuna tähistamist vajab ka Joonase seitsmes sünnipäev, siis on plaan külastada Põhja-Saksamaa kõige suuremat lõbustusparki, kus lusti jagub nii väikestele kui ka suurtele. Üllatuslikult avaldavad Anni ja Tarvo oma tulevikuplaane seoses mõttega elada mõnda aega ka Eestist väljaspool. Kesküllad kohanevad kõikjal kiiresti ka siis, kui majutusasutuses puudub pesumasin ja mänguasjad. Mängida saab ka köögisahtlites peituvaga ja samal ajal vähenevad mustade riiete kuhjad Anni töökate käte võluväel. Paaripäevane peatus Saksamaal möödub seitsme lapse, hulga kohustuste ja tähistamistega lausa silmapilguga.

programme.title: Õnne 13
programme.desc: Anneli ja Margna proovivad oma suhteid siluda. Evelin räägib Marele oma raskest elust. Rebeka on kõigi Filipi tingimustega nõus. Maria ja väike Maria kurdavad Henryle, et neil on aina raskem Evelini juures elada.

programme.title: Aktuaalne kaamera. Ilm
programme.desc: "Aktuaalne kaamera" on Eesti Televisiooni igapäevane eestikeelne uudistesaade.

programme.title: Sport. Sport
programme.desc: ETV toob teieni Eesti ja kogu maailma kõige värskemad spordiuudised.

programme.title: Davos 1917
programme.desc: Kui kindral Taylor Davosist lahkub, muutub Johanna Saksa salaluure jaoks väärtusetuks. Ilsel kästakse ta kõrvaldada, kuid naisel on varuplaan. Doktor Mangold püüab Johannat vastaspoole agendiks värvata. Segaduses Johanna nõustub edasi spioneerima, et vaid saada raha ja uus pass lapsega koos põgenemiseks.

programme.title: Ühe armuloo lõpp
programme.desc: Kirjanik Maurice Bendrixil (Ralph Fiennes) on teise maailmasõja ajal oma parima sõbra naise Sarah Milesiga (Julianne Moore) salasuhe. Sarah teeb suhtele 1944. aastal lõpu. Kaks aastat hiljem, kui Maurice kohtub juhuslikult oma vana sõbraga, tekib mehel kunagise kallima suhtes kinnisidee. Ta palkab mehe Sarah't jälgima. Tal õnnestub lugeda naise päevikust nende Londoni pommitamise ajal aset leidnud suhte kohta ja saab teada, et naine vandus jumalale, et lõpetab Maurice'i elu päästmise nimel nende salasuhte. Kuigi Maurice üritab taas leida teed Sarah ellu, ei soovi naine teda ligi lasta.

programme.title: Detsembrikuumus
programme.desc: 9. november 1924. Näib, et kommunismitont enam Eesti Vabariiki ei ohusta. Noor abielupaar Tanel ja Anna üritavad toime tulla Eesti sõjaväelase ning sidekeskuse töötaja kasina sissetulekuga, kuid otsustavad siiski sõita Pariisi paremat elu otsima. Samal ajal aga kogutakse piiri taga mehi, Tallinnas varjavad end mässulised, rahva hulgas töötavad agitaatorid. 1. detsembril, ärasõiduhommikul, lähevad Tanel ja Anna Balti jaama, kus leiavad end otse keset äsjapuhkenud riigipöördekatset. Mõlemad langevad mässuliste küüsi ja lahutatakse teineteisest. Anna satub pantvangi kommunistide liidri kätte, kellega teda seob ühine minevik, Tanel aga peab võitlema nii vabariigi kui ka oma naise päästmise nimel... Kas noor ja habras Eesti Vabariik suudab püsima jääda? Filmil on ka kirjeldustõlge.

programme.title: Ivalo
programme.desc: Soomes Lapimaal Ivalos teeb noor politseiuurija Nina Kautsalo kohutava avastuse ühest tundras asuva maja keldrist. Leid toob kohale viiruseid uuriva Saksa teadlase Thomas Lorenzi ning järsku leiavad Nina ja Thomas ennast väga ebatavalise kriminaaluurimise keskelt.

programme.title: Rick Steini salajane Prantsusmaa
programme.desc: Seekord viib Ricki rännak Prantsusmaa idapoolsetesse piirkondadesse, Alsace'i ja Juura kanti, kust on pärit tema kõige lemmikum Prantsuse toit, choucroute garnie ning lemmikjuust Comté.

programme.title: ERR.ee uudised
programme.desc: Eesti Rahvusringhäälingu uudised - Eesti ja kogu maailma kõige värskemad uudised.

programme.title: rus.err.ee uudised
programme.desc: No description available

programme.title: Reisikaaslane
programme.desc: Selle saate külaline läbis 1000-kilomeetrise teekonna selleks, et saada meie kaasreisijaks ja külastada oma lapsepõlvelinna. Võibolla ei tule tema nimi kohe meelde, kuid nägu pole võimalik unustada. Ekskursiooni enda minevikku viib läbi Venemaa rahvakunstnik Igor Jasulovitš, kes räägib, kus ta koolis käis, millises hoovis üles kasvas ning missuguse elamuse pakkus tema perekonnale Eesti aastal 1952.

programme.title: TECHnolik
programme.desc: Kuidas saab õhust elektrit? Kuidas energia mahub patareisse? Mida koguvad superkondensaatorid? Millal hakkavad robotid meid õpetama? Vastused nendele ja ka teistele küsimustele saate haridus-meelelahutuslikus saates, mis räägib uutest tehnoloogiatest.

programme.title: Kutsikate imeline maailm
programme.desc: Chihuahua-kutsikas Teddy läheb kostüümivõistlusele. Üliarmas berni alpi karjakoer Sasha külastab kohalikku turgu. Manchesteri terjeri kutsikas Miller armastab tähelepanu ja kiharakarvaline retriiver Winston läheb esimest korda järve äärde.

programme.title: UUS! Pikk nädalavahetus Rory O'Connelliga
programme.desc: Rory alustab oma nädalalõppu piknikuga paigas, kust avaneb imeline vaade Lissabonile. Delikatessipood Manteigaria Silva on Rory suureks rõõmuks tõeline Portugali toidu aardekamber. Ta külastab ka vana Conserveira de Lisboa poekest, mis on spetsialiseerunud kunstipäraselt kujundatud kalakonservide müügile. Reisilt inspiratsiooni saanuna valmistab Rory kodus soolaheiki õunapüree, röstpipra, palsamiäädika ja basiilikuga.

programme.title: Horisondi nädal
programme.desc: Valik nädala parimaid palasid saatest "Horisont". Sündmused, inimesed, nähtused, vestlused kuulsate külalistega. Eestist ja meid ümbritsevast maailmast.

programme.title: UUS! Erakordsed Šveitsi mägiraudteed
programme.desc: Šveitsi mägistel hammasraudteedel on tagatud majesteetlikud vaated erakordsetele mäetippudele. Unikaalne segu traditsioonidest, tehnoloogiast ja loodusest lummab huvilisi tervest maailmast sama palju kui saja aasta eest. Enamjaolt sõidavad neil raudteedel 19. sajandist pärinevad ajaloolised vedurid ja vagunid. Berni kantonis paiknev Brienzer Rothorn pakub kõige maalilisemaid vaateid Alpidele. Seal sõidab ka ainus igapäevane Šveitsi hammasraudteerong. Ligi 8 km pikkune raudtee raiuti 130 aasta eest käsitsi mäeküljele ja viib 2200 meetri kõrgusele, kus avaneb vaade rohelisele Brienzi järvele. Siiamaani sõidavad seal 19. sajandist pärinevad vedurid.

programme.title: Canterville'i lossi vaim
programme.desc: Kummitus sir Simon de Canterville on juba 300 aastat oma lossis elanud ja talle väga meeldib seal. Sir Canterville'i lõbustab lossi vahetevahel sattuvate külaliste kiire lahkumine, kui nad teda kohtavad. Kuid ühel päeval kolib vanasse lossi Otise perekond ja see seltskond on vanale vaimule šokk! Uued lossiomanikud ei karda kummitusjutte, nad peavad neid... natuke vanamoelisteks. Ükskõik, kui õudseid lugusid Sir Canterville välja mõtleb, meeldivad need perekonnale väga. Vana kummitus tiirutab oma lossis ringi, hoides peast kinni! Kuidas on see võimalik?! Otiste vembumeestest poisid, kaksikud Kent ja Louis, hirmutavad hoopis teda ennast! Ja saadiku naine, proua Lucretia, soovitab sööril oma kolisevad ketid õlitada, sest selle müra sees on võimatu uinuda! Sir Canterville on asja pärast väga mures. Kui asjad nii jätkuvad, kaotab ta igaveseks maine kõige hirmsama kummitusena! Ootamatult aga sõbruneb Sir Canterville pere noordaami Virginia'ga. Võluv kummitus räägib talle oma uskumatu eluloo ja siis algavad tõelised seiklused, mis on täis põnevaid üllatusi. Sukelduge kummituste salapärasesse ellu, avastage Oscar Wilde'i imelise ja müstilise teose maailm.

programme.title: Jälg
programme.desc: Linna lähedalt metsast leitakse salakaubanduse vastu võitlemise osakonna töötaja Vladimir Malinini väljatorgatud silmadega surnukeha. Tapetu lukustamata korterist leitakse aga teine laip, mille taskus on kaks silma...

programme.title: Jälg
programme.desc: Üliõpilane Ljudmila Larionova saab ootamatult päranduseks kaugelt sugulaselt maamaja ja sõidab pärandit vastu võtma koos sõpradega. Naabrite sõnul oli kadunuke olnud nõid, kelle vaim siiani valvab ta maja. Öösel toimub majas midagi kummalist ja selle tagajärjel leiab aset mitu mõrva. FET tuleb uurima "mustade jõudude" müsteeriumit.

programme.title: Jälg
programme.desc: Tapetakse filmirežissöör Kirill Olšanski, keda on enne surma julmalt piinatud. Kõik tõendid viitavad ta parimale sõbrale Olegile ja ta kallimale Alinale. Uurimise käigus selgub, et Kirill ise oli koletis ja ka ta kallimal oli oma varjatud pool.

programme.title: Jälg
programme.desc: FETi saadetakse liiklusõnnetuses hukkunud politseikapteni laip, et eksperdid toimiku kiiresti sulgeksid. Peagi selgub, et ka avariis süüdi olnud ärimees Ivlev on sooritanud enesetapu. FETi uurijad otsustavad paljastada kummaliste surmadega seotud niidistiku.

programme.title: Jälg
programme.desc: Noored sugulased kogunevad suvevaheajaks rikka tädi majja. Improviseeritud etenduse käigus saab surma näitleja Goša Amossov. FET-i eksperdid selgitavad välja, et majaelanikud sepitsevad vandenõu ja plaanivad veel üht kuritööd...

programme.title: Eestimaa kuulsad inimesed
programme.desc: Seitsmendas saates tehakse juttu rahvaluule- ja keeleteadlasest ning ühiskonnategelasest Jakob Hurdast. Autor Galina Velman, režissöör Sergei Ledenjov. Tootja MTÜ Vene Muuseum.

programme.title: Heateod
programme.desc: Paljud meid ümbritsevatest inimestest võivad esmapilgul tunduda täiesti tavalised ja jääda märkamatuks. Kuid kui me nendega lähemalt tutvume, siis selgub, et neist igaüks on eriline. Sellistest inimestest räägibki meie saatesari. Sarja esimeses saates külastame Päite loomaparki, kus on ajutist peavarju leidnud metskitsed, hobused, ponid... Tootja Osakond OÜ.

programme.title: Jääkütid
programme.desc: Dokumentaalfilm võtab vaatluse alla Kanadast alguse saanud äri, kus jäämägede küljest kogutud jää sulatatakse üles ning pannakse luksusvee sildi all pudelisse. Tulus veeäri on andnud uue hingamise varem raskustes olnud Kanada kaluritele, kellest on saanud professionaalsed "jääkütid". Ent jäämägede sulavee müümise mõju keskkonnale on tekitanud nüüd olukorra, kus ühe mehe õnn on kogu inimkonna õnnetus.

programme.title: Maitsev Elu ETV+
programme.desc: No description available

programme.title: Eesti Gloobus
programme.desc: Televiktoriinis "Eesti gloobus" astuvad võistlustulle telesaatejuht Alina Privalova ja tipp-juuksur Igor Zahharov ja nende vastasmeeskonnas on ajakirjanik Roman Starapopov ja Tartu Ülikooli tudeng Vassilissa Kovkin. Meeleolukates videolugudes seikleb Alina Zahharova interaktiivses teatrimuuseumis "Tallinna legendid", Aleksandr Hobotov külastab Porkuni Mõisa ja Jevgeni Zavadski räägib Kiiu küla vaatamisväärsustest. Saatejuhid Artur Tjulenev ja Natalia Demidova.

programme.title: Kordumatu Keanu Reeves
programme.desc: Dokfilm heidab pilgu Keanu Reeves'i noorusajale, filmograafiale ja elusündmuste kõrg- ning madalseisudele. Vaatajal on võimalus avastada, mis teeb tagasihoidlikust mehest tõeliselt tunnustatud superstaari. "Billi ja Tedi", "Matrixi" ja "John Wicki" peaosaline pole mitte ainult armastatud näitleja, vaid ka hinnatud heategija.

programme.title: Narva stuudio. Rahvale tähtis
programme.desc: Iganädalane väitlussaade, kus koos külalistega arutleme Ida-Virumaad puudutavatel päevakajalistel teemadel. Saadet juhib Mihhail Komaško. Saate toimetaja on Jevgenia Parv, režissöör Sergei Ledenjov, produtsent Heiki Sepp.

programme.title: Orbiit
programme.desc: Saates olulised nädala välispoliitilised sündmused.

programme.title: Sissi
programme.desc: Ertshertsoginna Sophie on otsustanud, et Austria keiser Franz Joseph abiellub Helenega, kes on tema õe Ludovika vanim tütar. Ludovika kutsutakse tütardega Bad Ischlisse keisri sünnipäevale. Franz Joseph ja Sissi kohtuvad juhuslikult ja armuvad teineteisesse. Pidulikul vastuvõtul kuulutab Franz Joseph kõigi üllatuseks, et kihlub Sissiga.

programme.title: Püha ämblik
programme.desc: Filmi aluseks on aastail 2000-2001 Mashhadis aset leidnud tõsielusündmused, mil tapeti jõhkralt 16 prostituuti. Iraani-Iraagi sõja veteran Saeed elab koos naise ja lastega Iraani vaimses pealinnas Mashhadis. Päeval töötab Saeed ehitajana, öösel muutub aga Pühaks Ämblikuks, kes prostituute tapab ja enda arvates nõnda püha võitlust peab. Teheranist saabub asja uurima ajakirjanik Rahimi, kes otsustab tapja püüdmiseks end ise söödaks pakkuda. Kuldse Palmioksa nominatsioon ja parima naispeaosa auhind Cannesis. R: Ali Abbasi, O: Zar Amir Ebrahimi, Mehdi Bajestani, Arash Ashtiani jt.

programme.title: Maailm pahupidi
programme.desc: Meeskond jõuab šerpade pealinna, Namche Bazari, mis asub 3440 m kõrgusel. Seal avastatakse kõrgmäestiku elukutsete eripärasid ja uuritakse šerpade üüratu jõu fenomeni.

programme.title: Maailm pahupidi
programme.desc: Dima uurib šerpadelt, miks ei tooda Everestilt hukkunute surnukehi ära. Lisaks külastab ta kooli, kus elavad ja õpivad nende šerpade lapsed, kes on hukkunud maailma tippu tõustes.

programme.title: Maailm pahupidi
programme.desc: Kuna Everesti nõlvadel dokumenteeriti esimest korda müstilise inimeselaadse olendi ilmumine, alustab Dima oma ekspeditsiooni lumeinimese jälgede ajamiseks. Talle saab ruttu selgeks, et kohalikud on lumeinimese olemasolus kindlad, kuid keelduvad temast rääkimast.

programme.title: The Lucky Dragon
programme.desc: A young, Chinese dragon punished by the gods to be a mere mortal is cast down to earth. He is forced to make his way in a strange land until the evil forces discover his true identity. Take part in a world full of imagination while following the journey of a mischievous dragon who has been transformed by magic into a little boy and exiled from his home to live among humans. When both good and evil forces learn that a dragon has arrived, they look for him as he is the only one who can find the magical sword—whose owner can rule the universe! Will he find the sword in time before it gets into the wrong hands? Will he ever become a dragon again?

programme.title: No Limit Kids
programme.desc: Ashton, Celeste, and Becca are three unlikely middle school outcasts who form a club in an abandoned theater. There, they meet Charlie (Bill Cobbs, Night at the Museum), a homeless man who shares their passion for musical theater. When the theater is scheduled to be torn down, the teenagers set out to save the landmark with a modern-day performance of Shakespeare's Much Ado About Nothing. Along the way, the group learns to treat others with respect and stand up for their beliefs. This Dove-approved film also features Emmy and Golden Globe nominee Lee Meriwether.

programme.title: Digging Into China
programme.desc: Harriet, a ten-year old girl, lives together with her big sister and her alcoholic mother out in the countryside. The family runs a motel. Harriet is different from the others, as she owns a great creativity and has nobody to play with. Her infinite world exists only in her mind. One day, Ricky comes along. He is a grown-up, but retarded son of an elderly lady. Soon, Harriet and Ricky share their experiences of life from a different point of view and become close friends. But his mother still plans to give Ricky away into professional care in a home, because she won't live forever to be there for him.

programme.title: Headwinds
programme.desc: Sarah tells Paul that she wants out of their marriage; the next day she disappears. A year later and Paul along with their children return to his childhood town to start anew after the loss of his wife and their mother.

programme.title: Baba
programme.desc: An weird but witty old woman is forced to deal with an ambiguous future after her country, family and the entire system of values are ruined. She is trying to solve her existential problems catching d trying to sell a rewarded war criminal as he was a rabbit in a wood. The only thing she did not know if he is really him.

programme.title: Among Thieves
programme.desc: Three friends - a reporter, an oil analyst and a financial executive - reunite after ten years and accidentally uncover one of the key, hidden reasons for what motivated the war in Iraq. The trio struggles to present evidence to major media that America invaded Iraq to force oil sales from the Euro back to the Dollar to preserve US global monetary supremacy. Against incredible odds, the team must face their pasts, find willing sources to corroborate the story, and survive the conspirators as they push to bring the truth to light.

programme.title: Wings Of Eagles
programme.desc: The continuing true story of Eric Liddell's glorious life after winning Olympic gold in the 1924 Paris Olympics. Liddell has returned to China, where he was born to missionary parents, modestly avoiding celebrity in order to teach local schoolchildren. In 1937, the Japanese invade China at the outset of WWll. Liddell with his friend Xu Niu, a street smart resistance fighter, recognize the increasing danger so Liddell sends his wife, Florence and their two daughters to safety in Canada. Duty-bound, Liddell stays to minister to the civilian victims. Liddell and other foreign nationals are taken as prisoners and placed in one of the many Japanese internment camps where they are forced to endure for two years. Before the Japanese surrender, Liddell succumbs to a brain tumor. Yet his message of hope became immortal. Eric Liddell's legacy continues to this day as he remains admired as a champion for life.

programme.title: 10 Rules for Falling in Love
programme.desc: A shy and sweet college dropout guy, Marco is in love. He lives with his friends and has a playboy dad. Is love art or science? Does it have any rules? Marco's dad thinks it has 10 rules and if a man follows them, he can get any girl he wants. An Italian comedy which was presented at the Golden Rooster and Hundred Flowers Film Festival (Chinese Oscar), in the section of foreign films.

programme.title: Saving Lincoln
programme.desc: The true story of Abraham Lincoln and his bodyguard, U.S. Marshal Ward Hill Lamon. This unique film features sets created from actual Civil War photographs.

programme.title: I Could Never Be Your Woman
programme.desc: Rosie, a divorced mother, lives with her daughter in LA. But her life is not exactly ideal. The tv show she has been working on seems doomed. Her ex-husband just had a baby with a younger woman, while her daughter has started dating boys!

programme.title: The Crash
programme.desc: In the not so distant future, a team of white collar criminals are enlisted by the Federal government to thwart a cyber-attack that threatens to bankrupt the United States of America.

programme.title: First Kill
programme.desc: In an attempt to reconnect with his son Danny, successful Wall Street broker Will (Hayden Christensen) takes his family on holiday to the cabin where he grew up. While Will and Danny are hunting, their trip takes a deadly turn when they witness the murder of a crooked police officer as a bank robbery goes awry.

programme.title: Open Door
programme.desc: A married Albanian mother and her pregnant sister try to find a man to play the part of the sister's husband before they meet up with their strict, traditional father.

programme.title: Perilous
programme.desc: Handsome young attorney goes to Russia for business trip where he meets young, misterious, beautiful and exotic Russian woman named Sasha.

programme.title: The Memsahib
programme.desc: British schoolteacher in 1850 finds love with the king of Begampur, India, but their love is cut short and their reincarnated spirits are reunited in Modern Day India.

programme.title: Почта
programme.desc: В почтовое отделение на должность экспедитора устраивается Елена (40 лет). Экспедитор Андрей (45) не очень доволен новой напарницей, он не доверяет женщинам за рулем. Но со временем между Еленой и Андреем возникает симпатия. И не без стараний со стороны их детей – Юли и Глеба. Андрей – одинокий папа, Елена - одинокая мама, казалось бы, ничего не может помешать их отношениям… Но тайны и ошибки прошлого сыграют с ними злую шутку… Бушуют страсти и в почтовом отделении. Руководитель отделения Артем (30) покоряет вершины почтовой карьеры и не желает замечать сотрудницу отделения Милану (25), которая мечтает заполучить его сердце. Мама Артема и его младший брат Гена также вносят в жизнь отделения свои коррективы… Все герои ежедневно сталкиваются с нестандартными ситуациями, но не остаются равнодушными к проблемам людей-клиентов почтового отделения, помогая им выпутаться из сложных историй…

programme.title: Верная подруга
programme.desc: В жизни учительницы музыкальной школы Кати Смолиной случается непоправимое – в автомобильной аварии погибает ее муж, Андрей. Лучшая подруга, которая находилась с ним в одной машине, в тяжелом состоянии попадает в реанимацию. Катя забирает дочку Инны, семилетнюю Машу, в свой дом. Сама Катя не может иметь детей и тем тяжелее она переживает гибель мужа – у нее ничего не осталось от их любви. Кроме того, свекровь осыпает ее постоянными упреками и обвиняет Катю в смерти Андрея – ведь именно она уговорила мужа отвезти подругу в оздоровительный лагерь к заболевшей Маше. А вскоре Катя узнает, что ее муж и лучшая подруга были любовниками…

programme.title: Нарушая правила
programme.desc: Главные герои мелодрамы "Нарушая правила" (2019) Марина и Роман приезжают в столицу в поисках лучшей жизни. Марина, имея высшее образование, берется за любую работу - и официанткой, и выгул чужих собак, а Роман сидит дома в ожидании высокооплачиваемой должности. Наконец ему повезло - предложили должность руководителя отдела закупок в крупной строительной фирме с хорошим окладом. Роман счастлив и даже не догадывается, что его наняли, что бы сделать повесить все неустойки и финансовые махинации. Когда муж попал в тюрьму, Марина понимает, то помочь ему можно только нарушив все правила большой игры...

programme.title: Авантюра
programme.desc: Лера давно разведена, одна воспитала сына-студента и уже забыла, что такое любовь. Но вдруг в ее поле зрения появляется яркий и харизматичный Илья Быстров, который окружает ее вниманием и заботой. Женщина и не подозревает, что чувство Быстрова - фарс, единственная его цель - втянуть ее в многомиллионную авантюру. Сможет ли Лера разглядеть проходимца, выпутаться из непредвиденной ситуации и после всего, что произошло поверить в новое, настоящее чувство?

programme.title: Почта
programme.desc: В почтовое отделение на должность экспедитора устраивается Елена (40 лет). Экспедитор Андрей (45) не очень доволен новой напарницей, он не доверяет женщинам за рулем. Но со временем между Еленой и Андреем возникает симпатия. И не без стараний со стороны их детей – Юли и Глеба. Андрей – одинокий папа, Елена - одинокая мама, казалось бы, ничего не может помешать их отношениям… Но тайны и ошибки прошлого сыграют с ними злую шутку… Бушуют страсти и в почтовом отделении. Руководитель отделения Артем (30) покоряет вершины почтовой карьеры и не желает замечать сотрудницу отделения Милану (25), которая мечтает заполучить его сердце. Мама Артема и его младший брат Гена также вносят в жизнь отделения свои коррективы… Все герои ежедневно сталкиваются с нестандартными ситуациями, но не остаются равнодушными к проблемам людей-клиентов почтового отделения, помогая им выпутаться из сложных историй…

programme.title: Страх в твоем доме
programme.desc: Боль и страдания, которые причиняют самые близкие люди, невыносимы. Дом из крепости становится тюрьмой. И в поисках выхода людям приходится идти на самые невероятные поступки. Ни один сценарист не сможет придумать такие сюжетные ходы, которые порой закручивает сама жизнь. В социальной докудраме "Страх в твоем доме" - только реальные истории, случившиеся с реальными людьми. Мы реконструируем события, основываясь на откровенных рассказах их участников, а наши эксперты - юристы и психологи - комментируют их и помогают найти выход из сложных, порой тупиковых ситуаций.

programme.title: Короткое слово нет
programme.desc: Они из разных миров. Тата – студентка художественной академии, Жека – вор и отчаянный авантюрист. Но эта история - не криминальный боевик или детектив. Это история любви. Настоящей. Такой, которая случается не у всех даже раз в жизни. Но им повезло. Они полюбили. И не повезло. Потому, что были из разных миров. Родители Таты делают все, чтобы разрушить их отношения. По следам Жеки идет полиция. Его арестовывают на глазах у любимой. Пройдут ли влюбленные испытания, которые выпали на их долю? Сохранят ли они свои чувства?
